description: Lists the workload deployment patterns for a given workload name. You can use the ListWorkloads operation to discover the available workload names.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The token to include in another request to get the next page of items. This value is null when there are no more items to return.

nested_items.name: deploymentPatternName
nested_items.description: The name of a workload deployment pattern.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of a workload deployment pattern.

nested_items.name: displayName
nested_items.description: The display name of a workload deployment pattern.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of a workload deployment pattern.

nested_items.name: statusMessage
nested_items.description: A message about a workload deployment pattern's status.

nested_items.name: workloadVersionName
nested_items.description: The name of the workload deployment pattern version.
